.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-CHANNEL-SUMMARY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-channel-summary \- high-level channel capacity summary
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-channel-summary
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns aggregate capacity, local and remote balance across all
.B CHANNELD_NORMAL
channels, plus average local liquidity ratio.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{total_channels, active_channels, total_capacity_msat,
 local_balance_msat, remote_balance_msat, avg_local_ratio}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-balance (1),
.BR lightning-node-funds (1)
